title: RussianEnglishTranslation
author: RussianEnglishTranslation
content: Q Blockchain, a new Layer 1 EVM chain focused on DeFi and Decentralized Governance, is jumpstarting DeFi on their chain by way of their "Q Saving and Borrowing Incentive Program". The program includes over 333k Q token rewards and an initial starting APR of 9999.99%. The program will run in three 21 day phases starting September 18th. There will also be a bridging bonus for users who use the Q bridge to bridge 10 USD or more of WBTC, DAI, or USDC to Q Blockchain plus an additional 5 Q bridging gift for any tokens bridged to Q.If you are interested in learning more about Q you can visit their website at Q.org. To join the DeFi incentive program you can join the waitlist at the following link- https://t.co/Y4hvDdidzJ
